{"he4a3135egdbb0g4829g9d43g8abb999bca02": ["We must not forget this night. True allies are few.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "04712d16-3ef7-4853-7a9c-669c2714688f"], "h3a886870gea14g42adgb558gca92589506f7": ["'Turn your back not to your ally, lest you would see it pierced.' So Vlaakith has taught us.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "ee121984-8ce3-9642-1755-95d1b92fc06e"], "h45c0b062g6ae2g4079ga5fbg4ec764925210": ["'Turn your back not to your ally, lest you would see it pierced.' A githyanki dictum.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "ee121984-8ce3-9642-1755-95d1b92fc06e"], "haffd09a1g5cebg42b0g82d8g93c0a825e1e8": ["A lesson you might have heeded, had your flesh not been weak.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "4d9da004-e64c-ef5e-945f-60a7e940b21a"], "h4657b9cdg9841g45f9g8aa1gbd573575fa6f": ["Associate as you wish. Indulge yourself at your own peril.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "e2c55580-02c9-a894-03da-402ad8c5ed79"], "h59da78faga5d1g4648ga5c6g28454a2b3c40": ["A lesson taught in flesh and bone this very night. Associate as you wish. Avert your eyes at your peril.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "3c27cdea-c201-5ff8-f500-fd0407433f3f"], "h64b6d66dgec89g415cga058g9e4d9458e1f4": ["Celebrate now. Come dawn, we depart.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "d711e64e-3d0d-4e74-8e73-79ee2842c846"], "hffa54835gaa57g4f92gb11bg6e0a9f7b4e6e": ["Soon. When you rest, I will come.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "2d679343-095e-8b92-503d-ea6eba4f7057"], "hffcde2f6g077cg4c00ga04ag1aeaca12046d": ["Celebrate now. Come dawn, we depart.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "07aac76e-d96f-277a-72f6-b83c2ef95770"], "h6b51bedag7141g4053g856dg99752229c14d": ["To think you might have known paradise.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "a7c86e12-b863-5a0c-5364-1683afee977c"], "h0564c144g5cc4g4a29gb5fega9071b0cd680": ["Celebrate now. Come dawn, we depart.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "b8b87974-f197-21dd-e50e-abece89df28a"], "hc538b372g2f83g4976gb418gaff8c72feeac": ["Mm. You have given in.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "66fa5624-6eac-7596-2ed6-6097dda75e4c"], "hed184b34gd344g44f8ga42fg053f8194cc6a": ["Yes, I <i>must</i> have you tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "a36aad56-e2bd-9e03-bc32-a9bff5f9888d"], "h9ddf48adgd41bg4995g85a1g95df9dbd4814": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "67270b00-f9c0-7587-0103-b4f1285f66b6"], "h05f4e42bg27a3g48e9gaf5dg31826d7788c4": ["I have seen the <i>kith'raki</i> tear a screaming neogi's legs from its belly to fashion into blades.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "9c1ba5e6-15a4-79ea-33c0-bd5f726a0b81"], "hc460a4eag142dg418ag8832g3452b0946f83": ["Yet they could not match your nerve today. It was enough to drive me to madness.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "47e96a5a-5cdd-6e9e-bb25-2963cd311de2"], "h280a9065g1992g4471gb508g59306c061961": ["I smell their blood on you still. I smell your sweat.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "172f4788-6814-4039-1274-c23ace9f1057"], "hd0039dbfgda9fg48c8g8f7fg6dbda3f2711d": ["I mean to taste it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "f74b273b-1cb1-8e9c-ff33-c7affec5bcc3"], "h0d1360e9gfc89g4986gac72g1c3f51de5333": ["I'll think about it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "d793916b-cd3c-6cfb-4c37-a126816a3555"], "h53c9a017gf649g406eg9263g33d26653bd27": ["You know the fortune of my company.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "66164aee-6afe-27e3-0d83-1fa8d777c039"], "h0eed64ddg8399g40e2g8856gd4a6a93e68ba": ["Another fortune yet stands before you. A warrior's flesh, rarely tasted.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "7784d085-f5d2-a0d5-c79c-f9ff5ca08aa5"], "h50df8531gc9e4g4195g896bgdf3c141c4b37": ["Bah - think if you must. The chance will pass come light of day.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "f5e708a1-3e43-453f-9849-95e25fe3f968"], "h49fdc4fdg72d1g41b4gbc3eg24879aabdbeb": ["Yes. Let our pleasure honour Vlaakith.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "29a634c5-27c8-c5c8-06d5-a95624e4233d"], "h681a1863gad47g45c9g87ebgb9a71aecbb13": ["Then taste it. I want you in my bed tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "29a634c5-27c8-c5c8-06d5-a95624e4233d"], "h1e31c81ag8ab4g4b7eg9b69g2cda8867331c": ["<i>Yes.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "25106c15-719e-b877-aae2-8d8c19a92e18"], "hd2726ec9g8fa7g4143gbcc2gd1d2d2f0b0cd": ["When you lie down for the night, I will come.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "aa9e338d-13dc-6bd9-f9f6-2e3b602a8ab0"], "hd1b8ca16g1a1eg4d2cga467g0d0cb6613bd0": ["And I <i>will</i> take what is mine.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "c8586d28-6057-3d23-fc0f-9d6d25a5e659"], "hb98b44a9g8d6fg44efga49fge94c91d7da4a": ["Are you asking me for sex?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "09d8b135-40fb-386e-85ce-f694f2e0496f"], "ha3e3d308gb761g48adg89b3g74629dd7e0e9": ["Yes.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "d1dd40db-612e-dd30-4f9f-074ec08442df"], "h05b102e7g7282g4a66gbe05g494b6a364a4f": ["Sex.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "f7dfcd78-3edf-2ab0-92e7-4492e866f8bb"], "h5473aee5g44bcg4fe2g9207g7d92fcef337f": ["A night such as this calls for flesh to feast on. And I have chosen the sweetest.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "320394fa-eae7-a3e8-41a1-fd3433e78f4e"], "hc8a421d6g8c0ag4735g81aegfd05c45c5418": ["No, I'm sorry. I don't see you as an intimate partner.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "a7cdd870-efa6-33a5-81bf-7252b5b6dcf8"], "h3301f7b8gcfb4g452cga04cgf9a555ae231c": ["I respect your error.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "14e5bb30-ac63-6b16-8943-33414fead82c"], "hfa109d67g128dg460cgb1a7g5f241e49c7ed": ["There are, after all, other spreads before me. Astarion looks particularly tempting tonight.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "233ca128-5971-53b5-9458-754f58aa1397"], "h8bef1b1agf7b7g4493gb38cg22872be17aee": ["I will not go long without pleasure.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "894af15c-2882-22d3-437d-51471d65733b"], "hcfdcf9c4g0ce8g48eegb9ceg9f319471e27c": ["There are, after all, other spreads before me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "50076644-a146-75d6-fd0e-b49898fec4cb"], "h75fe3e9dg146cg497cgb084gd92af5329788": ["A pity for us you have promised your body to Astarion.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "6c8de642-38ef-57aa-8157-b0375bab7ad7"], "h0cb1b8aag8dddg458eg84afg206c3aaba11f": ["I hope for your sake he doesn't come too near your neck.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "a656ba7d-04ef-205d-1b6d-f4eafb57572e"], "hfde8dc39g0461g4e88gb96eg5696de8e9e5c": ["Maybe another night? It could be sweeter for waiting.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "c36837ee-be17-d7f1-0810-e5f68292eaa1"], "hc2b548b1g666eg44bdgb94eg446903b4f6bd": ["Perhaps.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "77b72d4c-7a61-01d5-7b95-577ee4853b0f"], "h92fd0940g9e55g4976g8b0dgcab58d08b4d8": ["Perhaps not.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "03cdc05a-18e9-3e11-5f5d-f0f677222451"], "h13d5aad2gf391g4698gbaeega3fe270e1771": ["I will take pleasure when I wish, and from whom I wish. Astarion looks particularly tempting tonight.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "bc88c9dd-d66e-938c-9eb1-82625f5dcfc9"], "h016bd80cg6770g4b69g8d36g1adbd93bbb01": ["One day, fortune may favour you.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "5194a1b1-f2b6-6a22-de28-5a1afc928696"], "h0082851bgf4f5g4998g8331g0d92551b6e8e": ["I will take pleasure when I wish, and from whom I wish.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "54006d0f-0b29-db46-486a-973ad4e5e739"], "h9e319423gbe1dg4281g955bg629b07508bb4": ["You might still persuade me to share the night with you instead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "e386a186-8ed1-0aab-6fe3-d6ff184b84b1"], "h61098381g39dag498ag9c3bg383d8222321c": ["I will do no such thing - not when you have turned your back on me so often.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "332f4195-1446-95d9-469a-014963c12a6c"], "h6586b1c2ga792g4c10g8023g8811b8eed20b": ["But come morning, you will wonder.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "23cd4583-480e-adcf-54bd-4e50d8139b1b"], "he16d9eb0ga073g4471gbde9gaf680bf798a9": ["You will wonder how my lips might have tasted, how my fingers on your skin might have felt.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "2efb428c-7eeb-7175-8fd4-a02cec07734b"], "he83e913agd064g4befga25cg3c372ccb656e": ["Oh, but do enjoy yourself this night. I intend to, myself. Astarion looks particularly tempting.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "d75b1348-76da-5077-d523-8046c02290ae"], "hda0279d1g735ag4d78g9a23g6f6d981d4da4": ["Oh, but do enjoy yourself this night. I intend to, myself.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "23d24127-fb7d-4d3a-95b5-aa7c12ed0c0e"], "h715aa826g40c6g4834gb337g5cc9493d0053": ["I made my choice, Lae'zel.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "04877705-bf85-39d1-daf9-8c0d051e727b"], "hba5500e1g55beg4eecg8b13g9936516ef3ec": ["For now.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "2f5b5429-5478-0f11-d3ef-7d7f9ab794bb"], "h5134ae31g64e4g4753gbe59g0b4d6d4f0dfd": ["You are a gifted warrior. It was pleasure enough to fight at your side.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "4cb115d9-af03-5b3a-490e-02e2532d1639"], "h653f761cgfb58g493eg90d4g94b6069ab445": ["Vlaakith demands of me no less.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "1c66b8a1-ad16-e46d-1e03-31d79e0b9b72"], "h3b5141c7gcbe3g4ef6g8b2fgd2202ce1b3bb": ["Mm - if only I might lay claim to my proper trophy.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "b8aab1ee-c03d-d9e0-b85c-f217a24d9129"], "h430ed6f1ga9f1g424dg971bg5c09f766ee9b": ["Come morning, you will wonder.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "23936b1d-f4f2-d44b-18d8-030028558605"], "h3a06604fgab3dg4fb6g87c0g94ec3a8935b9": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "7e9f6460-3724-8303-7a91-ab3ab62d95f0"], "ha1afa004g440eg4cbag9362g7335c5ed186a": ["A pity for us you have promised your night to Gale.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "15965ef0-370f-fd67-4a57-3caa428be2f0"], "h37c115bcg2d33g4dfdg80bbg0c7611df0744": ["I've no doubt he will satisfy your tastes for endless conversation.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Laezel.html", "8